{"tid":1283274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再大肆報道義士跳樓新聞","createTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T09:50:42.000Z","uid":184370,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ff4eaffea775348a4608fd4a18617cd9932a5d","tid":1283274,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:39.000Z","msg":"我知道呢一個月內已經有好幾位義士為咗香港跳樓<br />\n大家既心情都好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔想再有義士死！<br />\n自殺呢個風氣係會傳染！<br />\n好怕再有義士見到呢啲新聞而有自殺念頭<br />\n希望大家唔好再大肆報道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位義士，你地要用行動去改變香港<br />\n不是用生命！！留返條命去睇未來既香港！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"b6c1e61a25c174b28beeb22552957d145aa2f5e3","tid":1283274,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5708181dfac5b145eb9612fba6c1723245f3e479","tid":1283274,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5ecb07cd35028e6937beb7ed7f3035b3a61561","tid":1283274,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fe25ea3fa26601b019ae220361f3fd757a1cd0","tid":1283274,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bfbef2bd481ebc436b5fdf9a9880bff845d609","tid":1283274,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1f1027649ef2619d8f4b94e5f5d43bf315ddcb","tid":1283274,"uid":88914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited